    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with the <strong>plant based 'Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cheese sauce mix</strong> to the pot with a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cooked macaroni </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1686239817801-x200.jpg",
