            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mix</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(use individual ones for fancy presentation!), top with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>veggie 'Nduja mac 'n' cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced ciabatta </strong>to a baking tray<strong> </strong>and put the tray in the oven for an initial 6 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
