    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>bruschetta mix </strong>– this is your<strong> bruschetta</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>veggie 'Nduja mac 'n' cheese </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
